389
00:47:27,940 --> 00:47:30,130
SPEAKER_22: We won't see him for a while.

400
00:48:08,539 --> 00:48:09,940
SPEAKER_22: He burnt it?

466
00:53:44,579 --> 00:53:46,070
SPEAKER_22: It can't be worth much.

603
01:10:16,140 --> 01:10:20,039
SPEAKER_22: Smelting steel is a duty.
