604
01:10:20,109 --> 01:10:22,810
SPEAKER_22: Mr. Niu praised us in front of everyone.

610
01:10:47,239 --> 01:10:50,569
SPEAKER_22: Must not be politically backward.
You can sleep later.

611
01:10:51,840 --> 01:10:54,670
SPEAKER_22: Are 15 dumplings enough?

723
01:23:05,510 --> 01:23:07,100
SPEAKER_22: I was telling Jiazhen...

724
01:23:07,180 --> 01:23:09,699
SPEAKER_22: that we could...

725
01:23:10,550 --> 01:23:11,979
SPEAKER_22: do propaganda shows.

726
01:23:12,050 --> 01:23:14,380
SPEAKER_22: Put these old things to new use.

742
01:25:02,220 --> 01:25:06,289
SPEAKER_22: Jiazhen's health is poor.
