743
01:25:06,560 --> 01:25:08,460
SPEAKER_22: We'll discuss it later.

757
01:25:56,750 --> 01:25:58,109
SPEAKER_22: He can run?

788
01:28:52,489 --> 01:28:55,220
SPEAKER_22: His leg's not so bad, and he seems nice.

789
01:28:55,859 --> 01:28:57,189
SPEAKER_22: I approve.

792
01:29:04,229 --> 01:29:06,430
SPEAKER_22: If it doesn't work out, we'll keep looking.

793
01:29:06,500 --> 01:29:08,659
SPEAKER_22: Anyway, it's up to Fengxia.

896
01:39:38,729 --> 01:39:40,699
SPEAKER_22: But it's Chairman Mao.

931
01:42:28,869 --> 01:42:31,340
SPEAKER_22: And will be better for your child.

1052
01:51:29,640 --> 01:51:31,470
SPEAKER_22: Who examined Fengxia?

1053
01:51:31,550 --> 01:51:32,770
SPEAKER_22: They did.

1054
01:51:32,850 --> 01:51:35,109
SPEAKER_22: You haven't seen any doctors?

1060
01:51:49,359 --> 01:51:50,760
SPEAKER_22: No doctors?

1069
01:52:28,369 --> 01:52:30,500
SPEAKER_22: We need an experienced doctor.

1070
01:52:30,569 --> 01:52:33,770
SPEAKER_22: Even if he only stands by, we would relax.

1112
