SPEAKER_22: Erxi's is a work-related injury.
It's not hereditary.

1114
01:56:38,119 --> 01:56:39,710
SPEAKER_22: Why not use this time...

1115
01:56:39,789 --> 01:56:42,119
SPEAKER_22: to think of a name for the kid?

1121
01:57:09,380 --> 01:57:11,250
SPEAKER_22: You just say anything!

1122
01:57:11,550 --> 01:57:13,250
SPEAKER_22: That's not a name!

1221
02:05:09,899 --> 02:05:11,289
SPEAKER_22: Little Bun...

1222
02:05:11,359 --> 02:05:12,920
SPEAKER_22: give me a hand.

1249
02:07:00,239 --> 02:07:02,500
SPEAKER_22: everything would've been fine.

1250
02:07:03,380 --> 02:07:05,739
SPEAKER_22: He could have saved our Fengxia.

1251
02:07:06,210 --> 02:07:08,369
SPEAKER_22: He's a professor, after all.

1255
02:07:19,060 --> 02:07:21,529
SPEAKER_22: People say, once you drink water...

